zone polygon evaluation, schedule checker, suppression\n- Local Kafka 3.6+ KRaft (no Zookeeper), 5 topics, Avro schemas\n- 30s clip extraction via memory-mapped ring buffer (15s pre + 15s post)\n- Edge Admin Console (Vue 3, offline-capable, 8 views)\n- Cloud sync with exponential backoff reconnection + 72h offline buffer\n- 5-tier bandwidth optimization for LTE (FPS/resolution/compression adapting)\n- Watchdog with 8 service checks + Prometheus metrics on `:9100`\n- Performance budget: <65ms per-frame (35ms headroom on 100ms target), 16×1080p@15FPS\n<<<END_UNTRUSTED_CHILD_RESULT>>>\n\nStats: runtime 3m40s • tokens 25.1k (in 12.0k / out 13.1k) • prompt/cache 33.4k\n\nAction:\nA completed subagent task is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type).\n<<<END_OPENCLAW_INTERNAL_CONTEXT>>>"}],"timestamp":1776801546355,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:2da63e29-30f7-427b-bf5c-4992cc4173db","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
