{"type":"message","id":"760767f5","parentId":"c668f8fb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T20:10:30.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give the user a final summary.","thinkingSignature":"34186c8157758aef2078173abe32966686baf122fc9bc0b862689d491e5b0284"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **s1-devops** hoàn thành + đã dọn directory lỗi!\n\n**DevOps Spec:**\n- EKS/Kubernetes architecture\n- Helm charts (safesight-api, alert-dispatch, event-processor, stream-handler, edge-agent)\n- CI/CD (GitHub Actions + GitLab CI)\n- Ansible for edge deployment\n- Prometheus + Grafana + PagerDuty monitoring\n- OpenSearch/ELK logging pipeline\n- Multi-region DR (ap-southeast-1 + Singapore)\n- Terraform modules (EKS, VPC, RDS, Kafka, S3, IAM, VPN)\n- S3/MinIO lifecycle policies\n\n---\n\n## 🎉 SafeSight AI - Tất Cả Specs Hoàn Thành!\n\n```\ns1-ppe-safety/\n├── SPEC.md              ✅ Architecture & Technical Spec (1,664 lines)\n├── PRD.md               ✅ Product Requirements\n├── architecture/        ✅ ARCHITECTURE.md (1,666 lines)\n├── backend/             ✅ FastAPI + PostgreSQL + Kafka\n├── frontend/            ✅ React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind\n├── edge/                ✅ Jetson AGX Orin + TensorRT + GStreamer\n├── mobile/              ✅ React Native (iOS + Android)\n└── devops/              ✅ K8s + Helm + CI/CD + Monitoring\n```\n\nMuốn tôi commit tất cả vào git không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":79,"output":318,"cacheRead":32644,"cacheWrite":1554,"totalTokens":34595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776802223249,"responseId":"06370cb0c08de2030283619e94247edc"}}
