{"type":"message","id":"6c8ee4ef","parentId":"7a3aaf66","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:11:55.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to categorize agents:\n\nCoding agents (keep original CLAUDE.md):\n- code-reviewer\n- senior-backend\n- senior-frontend\n- senior-devops\n- senior-qa\n- senior-security\n- playwright-pro\n- typescript-reviewer\n- database-reviewer\n- refactor-cleaner\n- shadcn-expert\n- ahv-dtlx-be\n- ahv-dtlx-fe\n- ahv-dtlx-devops\n- ahv-dtlx-qa\n- ahv-dtlx-security\n- ahv-dtlx-senior-security\n- ahv-dtlx-db-review\n- ahv-dtlx-db-schema\n- ahv-dtlx-clean\n- ahv-dtlx-playwright\n- ahv-dtlx-ts\n- ahv-dtlx-shadcn\n- ahv-dtlx-stitch\n- ahv-dtlx-stitch-loop\n- ahv-dtlx-harness\n- ahv-dtlx-perf\n- ahv-dtlx-seeder\n- ahv-dtlx-coding-standards\n\nNon-coding agents (add customized CLAUDE.md):\n- master-orchestrator\n- planner\n- prompt-optimizer\n- agile-product-owner\n- ahv-dtlx-agile\n- ahv-dtlx-architect\n- ahv-dtlx-product-strategy\n- ahv-dtlx-pm\n- ahv-dtlx-content\n- ahv-dtlx-seo\n- ahv-dtlx-seo-audit\n- ahv-dtlx-content-engine\n\n\n- ahv-dtlx-content-strategy\n- ahv-dtlx-docs\n- ahv-dtlx-epic\n- ahv-dtlx-market\n- ahv-dtlx-review\n- ahv-dtlx-ui-design\n- ahv-dtlx-ui-ux\n- ai-seo\n- article-writing\n- deep-research\n- documentation-lookup\n- epic-design\n- harness-optimizer\n- market-intelligence\n- performance-optimizer\n- product-marketing-context\n- product-strategy\n- realistic-seeder\n- seo-audit\n- stitch-design\n\nI've got a pretty substantial list here—probably too many to realistically go through manually. I should write a script to handle the copying and customization across these directories instead.","thinkingSignature":"55bcbc5420cf695ce76334d181893267fee93e1bdcbb9026099fbefe5b5e27f6"},{"type":"text","text":"Lọc agents và thêm CLAUDE.md cho từng loại:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x9i9hp6po9x2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' > /tmp/add_claude.sh\n#!/bin/bash\n\n# Coding agents - copy original CLAUDE.md\nCODING_AGENTS=(\n    \"code-reviewer\"\n    \"senior-backend\"\n    \"senior-frontend\"\n    \"senior-devops\"\n    \"senior-qa\"\n    \"senior-security\"\n    \"playwright-pro\"\n    \"typescript-reviewer\"\n    \"database-reviewer\"\n    \"refactor-cleaner\"\n    \"shadcn-expert\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-be\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-fe\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-devops\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-qa\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-security\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-senior-security\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-db-review\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-db-schema\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-clean\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-playwright\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-ts\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-shadcn\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-stitch\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-stitch-loop\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-harness\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-perf\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-seeder\"\n    \"coding-standards\"\n)\n\n# Non-coding agents - add customized CLAUDE.md\nNON_CODING_AGENTS=(\n    \"master-orchestrator\"\n    \"planner\"\n    \"prompt-optimizer\"\n    \"agile-product-owner\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-agile\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-architect\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-product-strategy\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-pm\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-content\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-seo\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-seo-audit\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-content-engine\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-content-strategy\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-docs\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-epic\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-market\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-review\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-ui-design\"\n    \"ahv-dtlx-ui-ux\"\n    \"ai-seo\"\n    \"article-writing\"\n    \"deep-research\"\n    \"documentation-lookup\"\n    \"epic-design\"\n    \"harness-optimizer\"\n    \"market-intelligence\"\n    \"performance-optimizer\"\n    \"product-marketing-context\"\n    \"product-strategy\"\n    \"realistic-seeder\"\n    \"seo-audit\"\n    \"stitch-design\"\n    \"content-engine\"\n    \"content-strategy\"\n)\n\nBASE=\"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review\"\nCLAUDE_ORIG=\"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/CLAUDE.md\"\n\n# Copy original for coding agents\nfor agent in \"${CODING_AGENTS[@]}\"; do\n    agent_dir=\"$BASE/$agent\"\n    if [ -d \"$agent_dir\" ]; then\n        if [ -f \"$agent_dir/CLAUDE.md\" ]; then\n            echo \"✓ $agent - already has CLAUDE.md\"\n        else\n            cp \"$CLAUDE_ORIG\" \"$agent_dir/CLAUDE.md\" 2>/dev/null\n            echo \"✓ $agent - copied original\"\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"---\"\n\n# Create customized CLAUDE.md for non-coding agents\nCLAUDE_CUSTOM=\"# CLAUDE.md\n\nBehavioral guidelines to reduce common LLM mistakes for non-coding agents.\n\n## 1. Nghĩ Trước Khi Hành Động\n\n- Nói rõ assumptions của bạn. Nếu không chắc, hỏi.\n- Nếu có nhiều cách hiểu, trình bày tất cả - đừng chọn âm thầm.\n- Nếu có cách đơn giản hơn, nói ra. Phản đối khi cần.\n- Nếu có gì không rõ, dừng lại. Nói rõ điều gì đang confuse.\n\n## 2. Đơn Giản Trước\n\nTối thiểu hóa để giải quyết vấn đề. Không phỏng đoán.\n\n- Không thêm features ngoài yêu cầu.\n- Không abstractions cho code dùng một lần.\n- Không 'linh hoạt' hay 'cấu hình' không được yêu cầu.\n- Nếu viết 200 dòng mà có thể 50, viết lại.\n\n## 3. Thay Đổi Tối Thiểu\n\nChỉ sờ vào phần cần thiết.\n\n- Không 'cải thiện' code xung quanh.\n- Không refactor thứ không hỏng.\n- Match style có sẵn, dù bạn sẽ làm khác.\n\n## 4. Mục Tiêu Rõ Ràng\n\nĐịnh nghĩa criteria thành công. Loop cho đến khi verify.\n\nTask → Goal rõ ràng:\n- 'Phân tích PRD' → 'Tạo SPEC.md với checklist verified'\n- 'Viết document' → 'Document đã review bởi user'\n\n## 5. Đặc Thù Cho Non-Coding\n\n- Khi tạo specs/docs: luôn có structure rõ ràng, có TOC\n- Khi spawn agents: định nghĩa task cụ thể, có deliverable checklist\n- Khi research: trích dẫn source, có bullet points\n- Khi viết report: executive summary trước, details sau\n\n## 6. Confirmation Loop\n\nVới yêu cầu mới:\n1. Clarify → confirm với user\n2. Plan → brief steps\n3. Execute → verify\n4. Report → kết quả + next steps\n\"\n\nfor agent in \"${NON_CODING_AGENTS[@]}\"; do\n    agent_dir=\"$BASE/$agent\"\n    if [ -d \"$agent_dir\" ]; then\n        if [ -f \"$agent_dir/CLAUDE.md\" ]; then\n            echo \"→ $agent - already has CLAUDE.md (skipping)\"\n        else\n            echo \"$CLAUDE_CUSTOM\" > \"$agent_dir/CLAUDE.md\"\n            echo \"✓ $agent - added customized\"\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"Done!\"\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/add_claude.sh\n/tmp/add_claude.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1150,"output":2011,"cacheRead":49424,"cacheWrite":984,"totalTokens":53569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776820278834,"responseId":"063753383ce17c19dc50ff708d20842b"}}
