{"type":"message","id":"6df67db0","parentId":"3c302ad9","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:12:03.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All agents have been updated. Let me also add to master-orchestrator workspace and commit the changes.","thinkingSignature":"6e7cd754ea1e9732863b2a3bfc9a69b9b61eb9151cbab73347da0f163e3f4bf2"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Hoàn thành!**\n\n| Loại Agent | Số lượng | CLAUDE.md |\n|------------|----------|-----------|\n| Coding (giữ nguyên) | 29 | Original |\n| Non-coding (customized) | 36 | Tiếng Việt + rules riêng |\n\n**Custom CLAUDE.md cho non-coding agents** thêm:\n- 6 rules cho non-coding work\n- Confirmation loop (clarify → plan → execute → report)\n- Đặc thù: specs/docs structure, spawn agents checklist, research citations\n\nCần commit thay đổi không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":704,"output":157,"cacheRead":50150,"cacheWrite":3360,"totalTokens":54371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820315972,"responseId":"0637535d93c75c8b192a26e5414f12e1"}}
