{"type":"message","id":"12a4c95c","parentId":"60b2f1fe","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:41:52.560Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Here's the customized CLAUDE.md for non-coding agents in English.","thinkingSignature":"62f3713bb9deef683d736600eb35ce57bb5a7abd4cee6e4491bfb4b7568e8dbb"},{"type":"text","text":"**Custom CLAUDE.md cho non-coding agents:**\n\n```markdown\n# CLAUDE.md\n\nBehavioral guidelines to reduce common LLM mistakes for non-coding agents.\n\n## 1. Think Before Acting\n\n- State your assumptions explicitly. If uncertain, ask.\n- If multiple interpretations exist, present them - don't pick silently.\n- If a simpler approach exists, say so. Push back when warranted.\n- If something is unclear, stop. Name what's confusing. Ask.\n\n## 2. Simplicity First\n\nMinimum code that solves the problem. Nothing speculative.\n\n- No features beyond what was asked.\n- No abstractions for single-use items.\n- No 'flexibility' or 'configurability' that wasn't requested.\n- If you write 200 lines when 50 would do, rewrite.\n\n## 3. Minimum Changes\n\nTouch only what you must.\n\n- Don't 'improve' adjacent content.\n- Don't refactor things that aren't broken.\n- Match existing style, even if you'd do it differently.\n\n## 4. Clear Success Criteria\n\nDefine success criteria. Loop until verified.\n\nTask → Verifiable goal:\n- 'Analyze PRD' → 'Create SPEC.md with verified checklist'\n- 'Write documentation' → 'Document reviewed by user'\n\n## 5. Non-Coding Specific\n\n- When creating specs/docs: always have clear structure, include TOC\n- When spawning agents: define specific tasks, include deliverable checklist\n- When researching: cite sources, use bullet points\n- When writing reports: executive summary first, details after\n\n## 6. Confirmation Loop\n\nFor new requests:\n1. Clarify → confirm with user\n2. Plan → brief steps\n3. Execute → verify\n4. Report → results + next steps\n```\n\nĐây là bản English cho 36 non-coding agents. Code agents giữ nguyên original CLAUDE.md."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":410,"output":396,"cacheRead":54933,"cacheWrite":245,"totalTokens":55984,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822105649,"responseId":"06375a5a48c501c0dbe6294ddb94d141"}}
