{"type":"message","id":"19bf1470","parentId":"c4556c31","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:45:56.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good understanding of both projects. Let me:1. Read the OTLXPA1 structure as reference (already have it from earlier)2. Create documentation pages in the AHVTEACHER space3. Use the confluence MCP tools to create pagesLet me start creating the documentation. I'll create pages for:- Overview- Backend Architecture- Frontend Architecture- API Documentation- Data Models- Features- etc.","thinkingSignature":"8b01532f8ff36a29b4b5ab29660e65237e519b811ccd3807d461784b277608c9"},{"type":"text","text":"Đang tạo tài liệu trên Confluence...\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9x7wljo8etie_1","name":"confluence__create_page","arguments":{"title":"AHV CMS Teacher - Overview","space":"AHVTEACHER","body":"<h1>AHV CMS Teacher - Project Overview</h1>\n\n<h2>1. Project Description</h2>\n<p>AHV CMS Teacher là hệ thống quản lý giáo viên và quản lý khóa học cho trung tâm đào tạo lái xe. Hệ thống bao gồm:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Backend:</strong> Fastify/Node.js API (ahv-qlhv-be)</li>\n<li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Next.js 14 (ahv-qlhv-fe)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>2. Repository</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Backend: <code>ahv-qlhv-be</code> - Fastify + MongoDB</li>\n<li>Frontend: <code>ahv-qlhv-fe</code> - Next.js 14 + TypeScript</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>3. Tech Stack</h2>\n<table>\n<tr><td><strong>Backend</strong></td><td>Fastify, MongoDB, Mongoose, TypeScript</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Frontend</strong></td><td>Next.js 14, React, TypeScript, TailwindCSS</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Database</strong></td><td>MongoDB</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Auth</strong></td><td>JWT, RBAC</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>4. Key Modules</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Quản lý học viên (Students)</li>\n<li>Quản lý khóa học (Courses)</li>\n<li>Quản lý lịch thi (Exam Schedules)</li>\n<li>Quản lý sân thi (Stadium)</li>\n<li>Thanh toán (Payment)</li>\n<li>Thông báo (Notification)</li>\n<li>Hỗ trợ (Support Request)</li>\n</table>"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":463,"output":604,"cacheRead":81477,"cacheWrite":406,"totalTokens":82950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776833146428,"responseId":"0637857b89547e473ebc003eb7c88b5e"}}
