{"type":"message","id":"d609f47c","parentId":"c7eda570","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:46:13.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It worked! Now let me create more pages for the documentation.","thinkingSignature":"faf5bb8663da752fe5e3a26a74afbcca7537c1c016cb29b23ccb117adbab3e6a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bvwdvd5yqkek_1","name":"confluence__create_page","arguments":{"title":"1. Backend Architecture","space":"AHVTEACHER","body":"<h1>1. Backend Architecture</h1>\n\n<h2>Technology Stack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Runtime: Node.js with TypeScript</li>\n<li>Framework: Fastify</li>\n<li>Database: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM</li>\n<li>Authentication: JWT with refresh tokens</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Project Structure</h2>\n<pre>\nsrc/\n├── domain/           # Business logic entities and interfaces\n│   ├── entities/     # Domain models\n│   ├── interfaces/   # Repository interfaces\n│   └── exceptions/   # Custom exceptions\n├── application/      # Application services\n│   └── services/     # Business logic services\n├── infrastructure/    # External implementations\n│   ├── database/     # MongoDB models and repositories\n│   ├── security/     # JWT, encryption\n│   ├── channels/     # Notification channels\n│   └── logging/      # Logging utilities\n├── interface/        # API layer\n│   ├── routes/      # Fastify routes\n│   ├── controllers/ # Request handlers\n│   ├── middlewares/ # Express middlewares\n│   ├── dtos/        # Data transfer objects\n│   └── docs/        # API documentation\n└── index.ts         # Entry point\n</pre>\n\n<h2>Key Modules</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>User & Auth Management</li>\n<li>Student Management</li>\n<li>Course & Lesson Management</li>\n<li>Exam Schedule Management</li>\n<li>Stadium Management</li>\n<li>Payment Processing</li>\n<li>Notification System</li>\n<li>Support Request System</li>\n</ul>"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":119,"output":414,"cache