Student management (Student model, enrollment, progress)\n5. \"4. QUẢN LÝ GIÁO VIÊN\" - Teacher management\n6. \"5. LỊCH THI\" - Exam schedules (Exam model, schedule management)\n7. \"6. QUẢN LÝ SÂN THI\" - Stadium management\n8. \"7. THANH TOÁN\" - Payment management\n9. \"8. BÁO CÁO\" - Dashboard and reporting\n10. \"9. THÔNG BÁO\" - Notification system\n11. \"10. HỖ TRỢ\" - Support request system\n\nEach page should include:\n- Mục đích (Purpose)\n- Cấu trúc dữ liệu (Data structure) - field names, types, enums\n- API Endpoints (method, path, params, response)\n- Ví dụ (Examples)\n- Luồng xử lý (Flow)\n\nUse HTML formatting for tables, lists, code blocks.","label":"ahvteacher-docs-be","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":823,"output":790,"cacheRead":89591,"cacheWrite":432,"totalTokens":91636,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776833344411,"responseId":"06378641430074ce50aa08eecdb38445"}}
