t the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type).\n<<<END_OPENCLAW_INTERNAL_CONTEXT>>>"}],"timestamp":1776833914879,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:19bb3c23-3cc1-40c2-ba1c-3c5a6529c3c1","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
{"type":"message","id":"393a1474","parentId":"ae9edd94","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:58:45.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The FE documentation agent has completed successfully and created 10 detailed pages. Let me summarize for the user.","thinkingSignature":"ca955c24d1a980c36499162d0e5754154b103f3b8a1a85fe6c3f2e601dc76116"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Frontend agent đã hoàn thành!**\n\nĐã tạo 10 trang FE chi tiết trong Confluence:\n\n| Page | Title | Nội dung |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| FE-1 | CẤU TRÚC DỰ ÁN | Next.js 16.2.2, React 19, Tailwind v4 |\n| FE-2 | TRANG CHỦ / DASHBOARD | Charts, StatsCards, RecentActivity |\n| FE-3 | QUẢN LÝ HỌC VIÊN | Student CRUD, filters |\n| FE-4 | QUẢN LÝ KHÓA HỌC | Course management |\n| FE-5 | LỊCH THI | Exam schedules |\n| FE-6 | THANH TOÁN | Payment management |\n| FE-7 | HỖ TRỢ | Support requests |\n| FE-8 | THI SÁT HẠCH | Map + stadium info |\n| FE-9 | COMPONENTS | Reusable UI components |\n| FE-10 | SERVICES | API service layer |\n\n**Tech stack phát hiện:**\n- Next.js 16.2.2 (App Router)\n- React 19.2.4\n- Tailwind CSS v4\n- Framer Motion 12\n- Chart.js 4\n- JWT auth with auto-refresh\n\n---\n\n## 🎉 TỔNG KẾT\n\n**Space AHV CMS Teacher:** https://dtlx.atlassian.net/spaces/AHVTEACHER\n\n**25+ trang tài liệu** đã tạo:\n- Backend: Models, Routes, Services, API Endpoints\n- Frontend: 10 pages với chi tiết đầy đủ\n- Deployment, Database Schema, Repository Info\n\nCần bổ sung gì thêm không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":171,"output":431,"cacheRead":92663,"cacheWrite":9058,"totalTokens":102323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776833914893,"responseId":"0637887c97f62108ef4a31a4ccbe034c"}}
