{"type":"message","id":"66c6ebe0","parentId":"358c34f3","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:16:17.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me create more documentation files for the other key pages.","thinkingSignature":"930ff914d514c5a05ead49f04aa318f5159a2d7fd90a0262a3e6ab2007ea50cb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2pez675vlp5f_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/ahvteacher-docs/1-BACKEND.md","content":"---\nconfluence:\n  id: \"130810201\"\ntitle: 1. Backend Architecture\n---\n\nh1. 1. Backend Architecture\n\n{toc:printable=true|style=disc|maxLevel=2}\n\nh1. 2. Technology Stack\n\n||Component||Technology||Purpose||\n|Runtime|Node.js|TypeScript execution|\n|Framework|Fastify|High-performance REST API|\n|Database|MongoDB + Mongoose|Document storage|\n|Auth|JWT + Refresh Token|Secure authentication|\n|Cache|Redis|Session, rate limiting|\n|Validation|Zod|JSON schema validation|\n\nh1. 3. Project Structure\n\nbc. src/\n├── domain/                    # Business Logic Layer\n│   ├── entities/            # Domain models\n│   ├── interfaces/          # Repository interfaces\n│   ├── exceptions/         # Custom exceptions\n│   └── types/              # Type definitions\n│\n├── application/              # Application Services\n│   └── services/           # Business logic\n│       ├── user.service.ts\n│       ├── course.service.ts\n│       ├── student.service.ts\n│       ├── exam.service.ts\n│       └── payment.service.ts\n│\n├── infrastructure/           # External Implementations\n│   ├── database/\n│   │   ├── models/        # Mongoose schemas\n│   │   ├── repositories/   # Data access\n│   │   └── migrations/    # DB migrations\n│   ├── security/          # Auth, encryption\n│   ├── channels/          # Notifications\n│   └── logging/           # Log utilities\n│\n└── interface/              # API Layer\n    ├── routes/            # Fastify routes\n    ├── controllers/       # Request handlers\n    ├── middlewares/       # Express-style middleware\n    ├── dtos/             # Data transfer objects\n    └── docs/              # API documentation\n\nh1. 4. Middlewares\n\n||Middleware||Purpose||\n|auth.middleware|Xác thực JWT token|\n|validation.middleware|Validate request body|\n|error.middleware|Xử lý lỗi tập trung|\n|rate-limit.middleware|Giới hạn request|\n|rbac.middleware|Kiểm tra quyền truy cập|\n|pagination.middleware|Phân trang response|\n|ownership.middleware|Kiểm tra quyền sở hữu|\n\nh1. 5. API Routes\n\nh2. 5.1 Authentication Routes\n\n|Path|Method|Description|\n|/api/v1/auth/register|POST|Register new user|\n|/api/v1/auth/login|POST|User login|\n|/api/v1/auth/refresh|POST|Refresh access token|\n|/api/v1/auth/logout|POST|Logout user|\n\nh2. 5.2 User Management Routes\n\n|Path|Method|Description|\n|/api/v1/users|GET|List users (admin)|\n|/api/v1/users|POST|Create user|\n|/api/v1/users/:id|GET|Get user details|\n|/api/v1/users/:id|PUT|Update user|\n|/api/v1/users/:id|DELETE|Delete user|\n\nh2. 5.3 Course Routes\n\n|Path|Method|Description|\n|/api/v1/courses|GET|List courses|\n|/api/v1/courses|POST|Create course|\n|/api/v1/courses/:id|GET|Get course details|\n|/api/v1/courses/:id|PUT|Update course|\n|/api/v1/courses/:id|DELETE|Delete course|\n\nh2. 5.4 Exam Routes\n\n|Path|Method|Description|\n|/api/v1/exams|GET|List exams|\n|/api/v1/exams|POST|Create exam|\n|/api/v1/exam-schedules|GET|List exam schedules|\n|/api/v1/exam-schedules|POST|Create schedule|\n\nh1. 6. Response Format\n\n{info}\nTất cả API responses tuân theo format chuẩn\n{/info}\n\nh2. 6.1 Success Response\n\n{code:language=json}\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"total\": 100\n  }\n}\n{code}\n\nh2. 6.2 Error Response\n\n{code:language=json}\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid input data\",\n    \"details\": [...]\n  }\n}\n{code}\n\nh1. 7. Error Codes\n\n||Code||HTTP Status||Mô Tả||\n|VALIDATION_ERROR|400|Lỗi validate dữ liệu|\n|UNAUTHORIZED|401|Chưa đăng nhập|\n|FORBIDDEN|403|Không có quyền|\n|NOT_FOUND|404|Không tìm thấy|\n|SERVER_ERROR|500|Lỗi server|\n\n----\n_Last updated: {date}_\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":97,"output":1124,"cacheRead":111013,"cacheWrite":1814,"totalTokens":114048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776834959158,"responseId":"06378c907acdc93bfc6a91a04fff3088"}}
