{"type":"message","id":"dbeab439","parentId":"be36a612","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:16:34.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me continue creating more documentation files.","thinkingSignature":"a4f3d13ff2fbdbbf06530fb7f7a4f5a331662f4b0c6ca214ab0d092fac97f51c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sli9sp84adfm_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/ahvteacher-docs/2-FRONTEND.md","content":"---\nconfluence:\n  id: \"130810216\"\ntitle: 2. Frontend Architecture\n---\n\nh1. 2. Frontend Architecture\n\n{toc:printable=true|style=disc|maxLevel=2}\n\nh1. 1. Technology Stack\n\n||Component||Technology||Version||\n|Framework|Next.js (App Router)|16.2.2|\n|UI Library|React|19.2.4|\n|Styling|Tailwind CSS|v4|\n|Animation|Framer Motion|12|\n|Charts|Chart.js|4|\n|Icons|Lucide React|latest|\n|Notifications|Sonner|latest|\n|State|React Context + React Query|latest|\n\nh1. 2. Project Structure\n\nbc. src/\n├── app/                          # Next.js App Router\n│   ├── (auth)/                  # Auth pages\n│   │   ├── login/\n│   │   └── register/\n│   ├── dashboard/               # Dashboard pages\n│   ├── students/                # Student management\n│   ├── courses/                 # Course management\n│   ├── exams/                   # Exam management\n│   ├── payments/               # Payment pages\n│   └── settings/               # User settings\n│\n├── components/                  # Reusable components\n│   ├── ui/                    # Base UI components\n│   ├── shared/                # Shared layout components\n│   └── modals/                # Modal dialogs\n│\n├── services/                   # API service layer\n│   ├── authService.ts\n│   ├── studentService.ts\n│   ├── courseService.ts\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── context/                    # React contexts\n│   └── AuthContext.tsx\n│\n└── utils/                     # Utility functions\n\nh1. 3. Pages Overview\n\n||Page||Path||Description||\n|Dashboard|/dashboard|Tổng quan hệ thống|\n|Students|/students|Quản lý học viên|\n|Courses|/courses|Quản lý khóa học|\n|Exams|/exam-batches|Quản lý lịch thi|\n|Sat Hach|/sat-hach|Thông tin sân thi|\n|Payments|/tuition|Thanh toán học phí|\n|Support|/support-requests|Yêu cầu hỗ trợ|\n\nh1. 4. Authentication Flow\n\nbc. ┌──────────┐     Login      ┌──────────┐\n    │  Login   │ ──────────────▶│  API    │\n    │   Page   │◀────────────── │ /auth   │\n    └──────────┘   JWT Token    └──────────┘\n         │\n         ▼\n    ┌──────────┐\n    │  Store   │  AuthContext\n    │  Token   │  + LocalStorage\n    └──────────┘\n         │\n         ▼\n    ┌──────────┐\n    │ Dashboard│  Auto-redirect\n    └──────────┘\n\nh1. 5. API Service Pattern\n\n{code:language=typescript}\n// Example: studentService.ts\nexport const studentService = {\n  getAll: (params?: QueryParams) => \n    api.get('/students', { params }),\n  \n  getById: (id: string) => \n    api.get(`/students/${id}`),\n  \n  create: (data: CreateStudentDTO) => \n    api.post('/students', data),\n  \n  update: (id: string, data: UpdateStudentDTO) => \n    api.put(`/students/${id}`, data),\n  \n  delete: (id: string) => \n    api.delete(`/students/${id}`),\n};\n{code}\n\nh1. 6. State Management\n\nh2. 6.1 Authentication State\n\n* JWT token stored in localStorage\n* AuthContext provides user state globally\n* Auto-refresh token before expiration\n\nh2. 6.2 Server State\n\n* React Query for API data fetching\n* Automatic caching and revalidation\n* Optimistic updates for mutations\n\nh1. 7. UI Components\n\n||Component||Purpose||\n|Button|Customizable button with variants|\n|Card|Container with header and content|\n|Modal|Dialog overlay for forms|\n|Table|Paginated data table with sorting|\n|Form|Input components with validation|\n\n----\n_Last updated: {date}_\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":95,"output":978,"cacheRead":111140,"cacheWrite":2849,"totalTokens":115062,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776834977051,"responseId":"06378ca2d8f8227aa8b1e875adf4324e"}}
