{"type":"message","id":"dc345ee2","parentId":"80b55f2c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:16:50.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me create more documentation files for the data models and API endpoints.","thinkingSignature":"91ce42b525b47e1970818b3a53712e95f14fcf455c25ed831499c694eaef4a0b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2rd9auwrvu3e_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/ahvteacher-docs/3-API.md","content":"---\nconfluence:\n  id: \"130842629\"\ntitle: 3. API Endpoints\n---\n\nh1. 3. API Endpoints\n\n{toc:printable=true|style=disc|maxLevel=2}\n\n{excerpt}\nDanh sách đầy đủ các API endpoints của hệ thống AHV CMS Teacher\n{excerpt}\n\nh1. 1. Authentication APIs\n\n{panel:title=Base URL}\n*Production:* https://api.ahvcms.com/v1\n*Development:* http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n{panel}\n\nh2. 1.1 Register\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /auth/register\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"username\": \"string\",\n  \"email\": \"string\",\n  \"password\": \"string\",\n  \"first_name\": \"string\",\n  \"last_name\": \"string\",\n  \"phone\": \"string\",\n  \"identity_card\": \"string (12 digits)\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh2. 1.2 Login\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /auth/login\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"email\": \"string\",\n  \"password\": \"string\"\n}\n{code}\n\n*Response:*\n\n{code:language=json}\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"access_token\": \"string\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"string\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"string\",\n      \"email\": \"string\",\n      \"role\": \"student|teacher|admin|...\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n{code}\n\nh1. 2. User Management APIs\n\nh2. 2.1 List Users\n\n{code:language=bash}\nGET /users\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nQuery: ?page=1&limit=10&role=student\n{code}\n\nh2. 2.2 Get User\n\n{code:language=bash}\nGET /users/:id\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\n{code}\n\nh2. 2.3 Update User\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPUT /users/:id\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"first_name\": \"string\",\n  \"last_name\": \"string\",\n  \"phone\": \"string\",\n  \"address\": \"string\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh1. 3. Course APIs\n\nh2. 3.1 List Courses\n\n{code:language=bash}\nGET /courses\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nQuery: ?status=active&teacher_id=xxx\n{code}\n\nh2. 3.2 Create Course\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /courses\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"title\": \"string\",\n  \"description\": \"string\",\n  \"duration\": \"number (hours)\",\n  \"price\": \"number\",\n  \"lessons\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"string\",\n      \"content\": \"string\",\n      \"order\": \"number\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n{code}\n\nh1. 4. Student APIs\n\nh2. 4.1 Enroll Student\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /students/enroll\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"user_id\": \"string\",\n  \"course_id\": \"string\",\n  \"enrollment_date\": \"date\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh2. 4.2 Get Student Progress\n\n{code:language=bash}\nGET /students/:id/progress\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\n{code}\n\nh1. 5. Exam APIs\n\nh2. 5.1 Schedule Exam\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /exam-schedules\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"course_id\": \"string\",\n  \"exam_date\": \"datetime\",\n  \"duration\": \"number (minutes)\",\n  \"location\": \"string\",\n  \"max_students\": \"number\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh2. 5.2 Register for Exam\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /exam-registrations\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"student_id\": \"string\",\n  \"exam_schedule_id\": \"string\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh1. 6. Payment APIs\n\nh2. 6.1 Create Payment\n\n{code:language=bash}\nPOST /payments\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"student_id\": \"string\",\n  \"amount\": \"number\",\n  \"type\": \"tuition|exam_fee|certificate\",\n  \"method\": \"cash|bank_transfer|zalopay\"\n}\n{code}\n\nh2. 6.2 Get Payment History\n\n{code:language=bash}\nGET /payments?student_id=xxx\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}\n{code}\n\nh1. 7. Common Headers\n\n||Header||Value||\n|Content-Type|application/json|\n|Authorization|Bearer {access_token}|\n|X-Request-ID|uuid (optional)|\n|X-Api-Key|api_key (for service-to-service)|\n\nh1. 8. Rate Limiting\n\n{info}\n* 100 requests/minute cho authenticated users\n* 20 requests/minute cho unauthenticated users\n{/info}\n\n----\n_Last updated: {date}_\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":96,"output":1187,"cacheRead":112860,"cacheWrite":2143,"totalTokens":116286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776834994167,"responseId":"06378cb3b112cd9b09e513fbf5cc57ff"}}
