{"type":"compaction","id":"2c44b359","parentId":"e5c63cf7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:25:28.891Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Continue monitoring master-orchestrator session (cron job every 5 minutes)\n2. Maintain Confluence connection for AHV CMS Teacher documentation space\n3. Support ongoing development work on AHV CMS Teacher project\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- All CLAUDE.md files for non-coding agents must be in **English only** (no Vietnamese)\n- Confluence credentials: email `ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com`, token `ATATT3xFfGF0bFjmIN6IPHwDzRChO8oMe5XAaA6dheluE8J2eUTNZHLgprik7oLx-vNnZsNVCb4cAAjziLDb27lKFHU2_RTgdeuv8zMkaPR-or2gSJQjHp8TMmOtI53F6MauTeaXX5Tg4gdMYyJ2nUKI-2HSMvK4TLkXLmKSKrdGrOpNDLRgMxA=8865492F`, URL `https://dtlx.atlassian.net`\n- Confluence MCP server URL must be `https://dtlx.atlassian.net` (NOT `/wiki` - server.js appends `/wiki/rest/api` automatically)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] SafeSight AI (s1-ppe-safety) specs completed via 6 agents (architect, backend, frontend, edge-ai, mobile, devops)\n- [x] Frontend demo running on `http://localhost:3003`\n- [x] Cloudflared tunnel exposed (URL changes on each restart)\n- [x] Pushed specs to GitLab `pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring` (develop branch)\n- [x] Setup session monitoring cron job at `*/5 * * * *` for `monitor-session.sh`\n- [x] Added CLAUDE.md to all 65 agents (29 coding agents = original; 36 non-coding agents = customized English version with 6 rules + confirmation loop)\n- [x] Fixed Confluence connection (URL had `/wiki` suffix causing 404)\n- [x] Pulled latest `ahv-qlhv-be` and `ahv-qlhv-fe` from GitLab develop branch\n- [x] Created Confluence space **AHV CMS Teacher** (key: `AHVTEACHER`)\n- [x] Created 25+ detailed documentation pages matching OTLXPA1 structure\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] None (AHV CMS Teacher documentation completed)\n\n### Blocked\n- [ ] None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **CLAUDE.md language**: Non-coding agents use English version with Non-Coding Specific rules and Confirmation Loop\n- **Confluence URL fix**: Changed from `https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki` to `https://dtlx.atlassian.net` because server.js adds `/wiki/rest/api` prefix automatically\n- **Session monitoring**: Uses `monitor-session.sh` script with cron every 5 minutes, alerts via Telegram\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Await any further documentation requests from user\n2. Continue maintaining AHV CMS Teacher Confluence space\n3. Monitor session health (cron job running)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **SafeSight AI project**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/version-demo/s1-ppe-safety/`\n- **AHV CMS repos**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/` and `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/`\n- **AHV CMS Confluence space**: https://dtlx.atlassian.net/spaces/AHVTEACHER\n- **Session monitor script**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/monitor-session.sh`\n- **OpenClaw config**: `/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- **Confluence MCP config** in openclaw.json:\n  ```json\n  \"confluence\": {\n    \"command\": \"node\",\n    \"args\": [\"/root/.openclaw/mcp-servers/confluence/server.js\"],\n    \"env\": {\n      \"CONFLUENCE_URL\": \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net\",\n      \"CONFLUENCE_EMAIL\": \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com\",\n      \"CONFLUENCE_TOKEN\": \"ATATT3xFfGF0bFjmIN6IPHwDzRChO8oMe5XAaA6dheluE8J2eUTNZHLgprik7oLx-vNnZsNVCb4cAAjziLDb27lKFHU2_RTgdeuv8zMkaPR-or2gSJQjHp8TMmOtI53F6MauTeaXX5Tg4gdMYyJ2nUKI-2HSMvK4TLkXLmKSKrdGrOpNDLRgMxA=8865492F\"\n    },\n    \"enabled\": true\n  }\n  ```\n- **Creating Confluence pages via API** (MCP tool has 400 errors, use curl instead):\n  ```bash\n  curl -s -X POST \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content\" \\\n    -u \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com:TOKEN\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d '{\"type\":\"page\",\"title\":\"TITLE\",\"space\":{\"key\":\"SPACEKEY\"},\"body\":{\"storage\":{\"value\":\"HTML_CONTENT\",\"representation\":\"storage\"}}}'\n  ```\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser (Khương Nịnh) added a new skill \"mastering-confluence\" and asked me to read it, check for any errors or unnecessary parts, and then rewrite documentation on Confluence while maintaining a Business Analyst role.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Found and read the skill file at `/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/SKILL.md`\n- Identified critical constraints: **DO NOT USE MCP for page uploads** (size limits ~10-20KB), must use `python3 scripts/upload_confluence_v2.py` instead\n- Found a typo in folder structure: scripts folder is named \"scrips\" (not \"scripts\"), and the upload script is named `upload_confluecne.py` (typo)\n- Installed dependencies from requirements.txt\n- Read reference documentation: `upload_guide.md` and `wiki_markup_guide.md` to understand proper formatting and workflow\n\n## Context for Suffix\nNeed to continue by checking current Confluence pages in AHVTEACHER space, then create and upload rewritten documentation with a Business Analyst perspective using the (typo-named) upload script.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/mcp-servers/confluence/server.js\n/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/SKILL.md\n/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/refereneces/upload_guide.md\n/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/refereneces/wiki_markup_guide.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/CLAUDE.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/version-demo/s1-ppe-safety/PRD.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/USER.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-22.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/monitor-session.sh\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/version-demo/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/vite.config.js\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"9f5246a1","tokensBefore":133019,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/mcp-servers/confluence/server.js","/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/SKILL.md","/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/refereneces/upload_guide.md","/root/.openclaw/skills/mastering-confluence/refereneces/wiki_markup_guide.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/CLAUDE.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/version-demo/s1-ppe-safety/PRD.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/USER.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-22.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/monitor-session.sh","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/version-demo/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/vite.config.js"]},"fromHook":false}
