{"type":"message","id":"a6448401","parentId":"6b0c5c50","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:26:09.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. Each page follows this format:\n\n1. **Metadata Table:**\n   - Target Release: [Page Name]\n   - Document Status: ACTIVE (Green)\n   - Document Priority: MUST HAVE (Red)\n   - Document Owner: VIETTQ\n   - Reviewer: ALL TEAM\n\n2. **Table of Contents (toc macro)**\n\n3. **VERSION CONTROL Section** with a table:\n   - A – Tạo mới, M – Sửa đổi, D – Xóa bỏ\n   - Columns: Date, Version, Người yêu cầu, Người cập nhật, Mô tả, Lý do, Ảnh hưởng\n\n4. **Content Sections:**\n   - I. DESCRIPTION\n   - ACTIVITY DIAGRAM\n   - SEQUENCE DIAGRAM\n   - WIREFRAME / UI DESIGN\n   - UI DESCRIPTION with a detailed table containing:\n     - Screen\n     - Function/Component\n     - Control\n     - Data type\n     - Require\n     - Condition\n     - Description\n\nLet me read one more page to get the complete structure of the UI DESCRIPTION table format.","thinkingSignature":"68ee668c7fe0c43fbeccff2032bda24dee29b8ea9730a081200619002392857c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0amfy24kd6gv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get the full content of 4.1 page for structure reference\ncurl -s \"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/524314?expand=body.storage\" \\\n  -u \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com:ATATT3xFfGF0bFjmIN6IPHwDzRChO8oMe5XAaA6dheluE8J2eUTNZHLgprik7oLx-vNnZsNVCb4cAAjziLDb27lKFHU2_RTgdeuv8zMkaPR-or2gSJQjHp8TMmOtI53F6MauTeaXX5Tg4gdMYyJ2nUKI-2HSMvK4TLkXLmKSKrdGrOpNDLRgMxA=8865492F\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys,re\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nbody = d.get('body',{}).get('storage',{}).get('value','')\n# Show HTML structure\nprint(body[:8000])\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2732,"output":523,"cacheRead":36565,"cacheWrite":4767,"totalTokens":44587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cac